013.query:
select min(ss_quantity)
       ,min(ss_ext_sales_price)
       ,min(ss_ext_wholesale_cost)
       ,min(ss_ext_wholesale_cost)
 from store_sales
     ,store
     ,customer_demographics
     ,household_demographics
     ,customer_address
     ,date_dim
 where s_store_sk = ss_store_sk
 and  ss_sold_date_sk = d_date_sk and d_year = 2001
 and((ss_hdemo_sk=hd_demo_sk
  and cd_demo_sk = ss_cdemo_sk
  and cd_marital_status = '@param0'
  and cd_education_status = '@param1'
  and ss_sales_price between 100.00 and 150.00
  and hd_dep_count = 3
     )or
     (ss_hdemo_sk=hd_demo_sk
  and cd_demo_sk = ss_cdemo_sk
  and cd_marital_status = '@param2'
  and cd_education_status = '@param3'
  and ss_sales_price between 50.00 and 100.00
  and hd_dep_count = 1
     ) or
     (ss_hdemo_sk=hd_demo_sk
  and cd_demo_sk = ss_cdemo_sk
  and cd_marital_status = '@param4'
  and cd_education_status = '@param5'
  and ss_sales_price between 150.00 and 200.00
  and hd_dep_count = 1
     ))
 and((ss_addr_sk = ca_address_sk
  and ca_country = 'United States'
  and ca_state in ('@param6')
  and ss_net_profit between 100 and 200
     ) or
     (ss_addr_sk = ca_address_sk
  and ca_country = 'United States'
  and ca_state in ('@param7')
  and ss_net_profit between 150 and 300
     ) or
     (ss_addr_sk = ca_address_sk
  and ca_country = 'United States'
  and ca_state in ('@param8')
  and ss_net_profit between 50 and 250
     ))
;
